                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/7254" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">STR-1810</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8608 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">多点发力，化“险”为“机”：华友钴业据“锂”力 争的转型之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Multi-pronged approach to turn risk into opportunity:Hua you cobalt industry to strive for the transformation of lithium industry</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">潘雪艳，李梦琪，屈博宇</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">安徽师范大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">浙江华友钴业股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">能源工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">营销部门/资本运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">11 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">决策型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">华友钴业；新能源行业；企业转型；锂电材料</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Huayou Cobalt industry、new energy industry、enterprise transformation、 Lithium materials</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本案例描述了在全球新能源行业如火如荼的势头中，新能源材料企业如何在大潮流中赶上分蛋糕的机遇，作为新能源行业中必不可少的动力原材料钴金属更是成为全球都在争夺的资源，华友钴业察觉到钴时代的到来，利用自身掌握资源优势发展成为国内钴业龙头，但是面对国际大环境争夺资源、国内钴矿储量少的以及非洲局势不稳定的严峻挑战，华友钴业重整旗鼓在自身拥有钴话语权资源的基础上敢于扩展下游产业链，整合上游资源，提高自身创新技术、拓宽下游销售渠道，以完善上中下游完整产业链布局，降低企业发展成本，走向了由资源型业务向资源整合一体化转型的“革新之路”。本案例旨在引导学生系统解读和研究资源型企业的发展路径、亟需转型的成因及契机和转型之后业绩表现，帮助学生了解企业战略转型的契机，提高学生的决策分析能力。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">This case describes the flourishing momentum in the global new energy industry, new energy materials enterprises how to catch the opportunity of dividing a cake in the trend, as a indispensable power cobalt metal raw material of new energy vehicles has become the world in the competition for resources, the advent of the era of Huayou cobalt industry aware of cobalt, using their own resources advantages to develop into domestic cobalt industry being leading&#160;enterprise,&#160; But in the face of international environment for the less resources, domestic cobalt ore reserves and the challenge of the instability of the African, Huayou cobalt industry regrouped in cobalt say its own resources to expand on the basis of the downstream industry chain, integration of upstream resources, to improve their technology innovation, broaden the downstream sales channels, to improve on the middle and lower reaches of the complete industry chain layout, reduce the cost of enterprise development,&#160; It has moved towards the &quot;innovation road&quot; of transformation from resource-based business to resource integration.This case aims to guide students to systematically interpret and study the development path, The cause and opportunity of urgent transformation and the performance after transformation ,help students understand the opportunities of strategic transformation of enterprises, and improve their decision-making and analysis ability.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《战略管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">风险管理；战略转型动因、PEST分析；战略制定、战略实施；四大能力指标分析</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023-03</td>
                            </tr>
